&#13;
<p>Are you on the right side of U.S. growth and reflation? To sum up the S&amp;P 500 sectors' leaders versus laggards for the month of May, <strong>Energy</strong> (XLE) stocks (i.e. Reflation) were down -3.5% versus <strong>Tech</strong> (XLK) stocks up +3.9% (i.e. U.S. growth accelerating exposure).</p>&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
